<body>
    <h1>T2 - Technical Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"a6a78739b23b" id=3D"T2-TechnicalDocument-1.Introduc=
tion">1. Introduction</h1>
<p local-id=3D"b4b04aa57ff4"><strong>1.1 Purpose</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"b4d61c810ac3">This document presents the technical design an=
d implementation of an automated infrastructure lifecycle management soluti=
on using AWS and Jenkins.</p>
<p local-id=3D"92d4643114bf">The objective of this document is to:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"858d1ffc-b121-4a7c-bdec-87180493f2e9">
<li local-id=3D"a36df45d-344f-4f7f-a4fc-fc0047bf92d5">
<p local-id=3D"ff1427f2f8ff">Demonstrate secure automation of AWS infrastru=
cture</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"70a9606a-5159-4df9-94e5-1bfa3c112412">
<p local-id=3D"694375318741">Explain the architectural design and implement=
ation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"228f6bf4-48bb-4056-9a01-f10e6e527f22">
<p local-id=3D"b53cf46706b5">Provide operational and security visibility to=
 stakeholders</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"391ccb65b44e"><strong>Intended Audience:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"a6bb76a9-15be-4040-8421-c34057849529">
<li local-id=3D"52b651cf-0b89-4cdf-b4f0-e5670efd15b6">
<p local-id=3D"a3c5fb1eb146">CTO</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8a692e27-b10d-4480-9816-458ecc0a10b5">
<p local-id=3D"9c30277feb72">Solution Architects</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"605a7db0-7be8-42f9-a8b2-884e9adf3c8f">
<p local-id=3D"d36ded5a6f32">DevOps Engineers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c9d99eb1-1c95-4e0a-9c83-76c0b00a4a13">
<p local-id=3D"2a6a7dbbc612">Cloud Operations Teams</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"46e75e50-4f93-4757-9352-bf7bc22d5959">
<p local-id=3D"852de736577e">Technical Resellers</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"4adec5a2-28be-47f7-9670-31e23d3a7cd9">
<p local-id=3D"83e6caae4068"><strong>1.2 Scope</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"836c137a8004">This document covers:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"f53e71e5-37cc-432f-8a59-525979ddc0d4">
<li local-id=3D"9003e724-28be-4770-87cb-e9beb291ae27">
<p local-id=3D"ead6c75bd47b">Provisioning and tagging of EC2 instances (Dev=
 &amp; Prod)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"204dcda5-5a08-4820-a76f-3d5cd88c1453">
<p local-id=3D"68911177e39d">Installation and configuration of Jenkins on E=
C2</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e3f65645-ef9d-4b7e-a985-02b59df69b7f">
<p local-id=3D"4e94766e85b2">IAM role-based authentication for Jenkins</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"f472863c-1483-4048-9025-534bd0956335">
<p local-id=3D"f7008fae778e">Automation of EC2 start and stop operations</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"6debb430-f8e7-43e0-9665-057149e24b3f">
<p local-id=3D"4cc7b5a82b8f">Deployment of ECS Fargate cluster and service<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e4c21d44-887d-420f-9519-b4728eac16a3">
<p local-id=3D"d569659f268a">Automation of ECS service scaling (desired tas=
k count adjustment)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9d919309-ffb7-4feb-83cb-ea07147c5520">
<p local-id=3D"7d768ccad139">Security and cost optimization practices imple=
mented</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"a3ade0ca99cf">This document strictly reflects the implemente=
d solution.</p>
<h1 local-id=3D"2bfd965553ea" id=3D"T2-TechnicalDocument-2.OverviewofDevOps=
Project">2. Overview of DevOps Project</h1>
<p local-id=3D"58265611f649"><strong>2.1 Definition</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"583a4d01c23a">The DevOps project focuses on automating infra=
structure lifecycle operations using Jenkins integrated with AWS services.<=
/p>
<p local-id=3D"be663a7e36bf">The implemented solution enables:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"50fce0fb-27c6-4b13-b6f2-4d3b14cf8c17">
<li local-id=3D"f94848ed-34e4-4d79-9397-c3271061f1ab">
<p local-id=3D"e3ee776e0f0b">Automated control of EC2 instance states</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"84af3346-bcb6-4642-bf16-c7b3adfa2348">
<p local-id=3D"3d7e498a2478">Automated scaling control of ECS Fargate servi=
ces</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1da1c1a3-0188-4003-bd3c-a18779e424be">
<p local-id=3D"1e0830b54dac">Secure infrastructure access using IAM roles</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2eb02a1a-dd7a-4ca9-a903-8485ec40d106">
<p local-id=3D"9a1e0c4e9881">Reduction of manual operational effort</p></li=
>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"374c34142f09"><strong>Benefits Achieved:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"39d5a9f8-5ab0-483e-8c8c-0a8427d35625">
<li local-id=3D"1eb2bb4b-8edd-41e1-b6e5-c3565cab72bb">
<p local-id=3D"0d61091bd67e">Standardized infrastructure control</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"92a09314-a822-4efb-b5e4-e518c504dfba">
<p local-id=3D"88330ad2ff2c">Reduced manual intervention</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fe151399-3624-4c34-b0ef-629a6361f259">
<p local-id=3D"56388e4119da">Secure authentication model</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2e33310f-aa0c-462c-a669-630eec8e4072">
<p local-id=3D"967eea37ff6e">Cost-efficient resource usage</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"0cb2fe08-d11a-4117-ae38-f3b72e8f8c84">
<p local-id=3D"11f7ebb3a554"><strong>2.2 Key Principles =E2=80=93 AWS Well-=
Architected Framework</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"78ad79bdb7fd">The solution aligns with the six pillars of th=
e AWS Well-Architected Framework:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"338455797e57">
<li local-id=3D"dd89212890b8">
<p local-id=3D"5ff82fe3300b"><strong>Operational Excellence</strong></p></l=
i>
</ol>
<ul local-id=3D"0477964c-eb8e-4871-ba27-1355baa1fedd">
<li local-id=3D"d296824d-c652-4520-b159-afd97813e37a">
<p local-id=3D"88c562bf6e11">Automation through Jenkins pipelines</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d2769ff7-0437-4fe4-8b77-b8d4cd32f726">
<p local-id=3D"c234595dca84">Repeatable execution</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3912b5a1-08b5-45f6-97cd-574d5de65b87">
<p local-id=3D"e79295573f2c">Build logs for auditability</p></li>
</ul>
<ol start=3D"2" local-id=3D"b505aacefab0">
<li local-id=3D"bc5d53cc1983">
<p local-id=3D"6d31eee35c4e"><strong>Security</strong></p></li>
</ol>
<ul local-id=3D"446fd260-de0f-4c2b-820a-f9f2ae13bbb1">
<li local-id=3D"48bfd0ea-ef23-4705-ac4c-d3c8f6d580fa">
<p local-id=3D"d4723bd83cc9">IAM role-based authentication</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"50e0bbd3-9a19-4d6f-836a-6c498423415f">
<p local-id=3D"6435b97a2ce3">No static credentials stored</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c179c8b3-49cb-44e3-9ed0-8efe7916078d">
<p local-id=3D"ff39cb9a3801">Least privilege policies</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3549e8c9-27a7-4294-a699-b60a05296653">
<p local-id=3D"8b061b3b4901">Environment separation via tagging</p></li>
</ul>
<ol start=3D"3" local-id=3D"35b7fc1e06a5">
<li local-id=3D"0989ffd47e2b">
<p local-id=3D"efee819bfbcb"><strong>Reliability</strong></p></li>
</ol>
<ul local-id=3D"bbef4920-c9a7-4fab-8c64-5724553e4f29">
<li local-id=3D"1f2d8f36-aa7d-4ce2-a881-4b167932e660">
<p local-id=3D"1daf8cb18830">AWS-managed ECS runtime</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1d53a8d6-3913-49da-8d0a-dc5634e57241">
<p local-id=3D"eb17dfa20a47">Controlled state transitions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b985c4fa-9780-44a6-861f-bb82fc756090">
<p local-id=3D"52a74149e26a">Verified task scaling</p></li>
</ul>
<ol start=3D"4" local-id=3D"0cb58656d1ad">
<li local-id=3D"7e897f51e168">
<p local-id=3D"60f97c2cb2df"><strong>Performance Efficiency</strong></p></l=
i>
</ol>
<ul local-id=3D"c0d678ee-19c9-440b-88e8-9cd4009bac7e">
<li local-id=3D"bd2bcceb-29ec-4449-96c9-c0bd007d067c">
<p local-id=3D"3d0a21d29605">Fargate serverless architecture</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a4756c87-1bbe-4fb3-9bd0-52e6820bd298">
<p local-id=3D"81da803fa205">On-demand scaling</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d50230db-f1c4-40ab-9a74-b02292898f5f">
<p local-id=3D"bbfb9271ebef">Dynamic EC2 activation</p></li>
</ul>
<ol start=3D"5" local-id=3D"d64ce79a897c">
<li local-id=3D"46dfd551f45f">
<p local-id=3D"ffafd1b7b8bd"><strong>Cost Optimization</strong></p></li>
</ol>
<ul local-id=3D"04936d6c-ec2c-4901-8c21-33e13d5b75d5">
<li local-id=3D"66110194-dbe7-448a-a110-53b2a383b137">
<p local-id=3D"0ca0049c80b3">EC2 instances stopped when not required</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"9ed441a3-dc6c-430e-8a6f-0f5431d397a7">
<p local-id=3D"03b57b6a8ad4">ECS services scaled to zero when idle</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5d151696-c93a-4bf5-983e-527f19c12a7d">
<p local-id=3D"9c4bd1b9e289">Avoidance of unnecessary compute runtime</p></=
li>
</ul>
<ol start=3D"6" local-id=3D"cf2e2dfe1213">
<li local-id=3D"c2ba4afc09f8">
<p local-id=3D"5000c7700f0b"><strong>Sustainability</strong></p></li>
</ol>
<ul local-id=3D"6b6b3d1a-287b-4812-b62b-4b846189a7d1">
<li local-id=3D"935ab76b-0fbb-48a8-807f-00997b234ea4">
<p local-id=3D"81d184cf5d96">Reduced idle infrastructure usage</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b08c42a1-264b-4f53-a9f4-54355ade9577">
<p local-id=3D"b60f8c3c174a">Efficient serverless container model</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"64675915-0c5f-4ae7-9f8d-e90781310256">
<p local-id=3D"06a6ec5c0021">Resource optimization</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"3e659515-2a29-491b-b9d1-dd988d3e5df6">
<p local-id=3D"6d08fcf6aa8c"><strong>2.3 Goals and Objectives</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"efe5ba6d9e52">The primary objectives achieved:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"d9a8d828-9e15-418e-9098-14f46410310a">
<li local-id=3D"e1fb2abc-c5e4-4a44-b64f-cdbfc8e35c20">
<p local-id=3D"7b0c6f9751fb">Automate infrastructure start/stop operations<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fb653434-ef40-4313-9e60-caa01db0604d">
<p local-id=3D"7b364beaf05a">Implement secure AWS authentication via IAM ro=
le</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6016adc7-c7fb-44af-a576-0a3f8d20a918">
<p local-id=3D"33f92718aba0">Enable environment-based control (Dev and Prod=
)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1aea891f-1fde-47ae-b66a-da12a266907c">
<p local-id=3D"b0da1210b5e7">Automate ECS Fargate service scaling</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"338ad899-b92e-47e7-b3b9-e2a87b04ab60">
<p local-id=3D"65e3937e0f98">Provide operational visibility via Jenkins log=
s</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"79a69540-c3b8-4fbb-8fdb-ef1eace27025">
<p local-id=3D"1283ef221c14"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"d1cf05e5b9ea"><strong>2.4 Constraints and Assumptions</stron=
g></p>
<p local-id=3D"937019172b06"><strong>Constraints</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"a662b8e9-44c3-4edd-97ef-6b6aa5c815d0">
<li local-id=3D"1b233f8b-dbd1-4c76-9e69-6707ef3d8372">
<p local-id=3D"4abb7df829f7">Lab-based AWS environment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ce0212a8-c678-4e91-a723-94c6a4475f42">
<p local-id=3D"28b0399c5624">Limited compute instance sizing</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d58f0bf3-32da-4785-b268-376cb4952bfd">
<p local-id=3D"c1f54c878ded">Time-bound implementation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c8ed3bd5-4621-4b85-8098-82fd6e1cd050">
<p local-id=3D"88d0e5c44c99">Use of AWS managed services only</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"55fa27533b05"><strong>Assumptions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"6a1ae796-47ea-46d8-a3e3-48ea60f55462">
<li local-id=3D"6578866a-aa8b-414d-8015-e92685614e29">
<p local-id=3D"725529a2f4f2">Default VPC networking</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"410ce3e3-1bab-4801-8b72-03ca005a59bd">
<p local-id=3D"b7849a882890">IAM roles permitted</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f8ecf983-5634-451b-b48f-e96cfda2f7ed">
<p local-id=3D"8cba206ba959">Jenkins hosted on EC2</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"373a2f8b-3121-4c02-9715-5e1d1aa4f5ce">
<p local-id=3D"166acf582fa3">Single AWS region (us-east-1)</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"3f049f91-3d6f-468f-8e78-de9dce457035">
<h1 local-id=3D"392131f00c9b" id=3D"T2-TechnicalDocument-3.ArchitectureandI=
nfrastructure">3. Architecture and Infrastructure</h1>
<h3 local-id=3D"2ca94b0d63a8" id=3D"T2-TechnicalDocument-AWSArchitectureDia=
gram">AWS Architecture Diagram</h3>
<p local-id=3D"93dc8b425f0d"></p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wr=
apper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"c=
onfluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"diagram-export-3-5-2026-12_28=
_30-AM-20260304-190528.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"836c3c39f=
b92188c8682eee30a109243cede7cfa87ce4913a71b66c4d481e0da" data-image-src=3D"=
https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1785331727/diagram-e=
xport-3-5-2026-12_28_30-AM-20260304-190528.png?version=3D1&amp;modification=
Date=3D1772651149387&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"814"=
