<p local-id=3D"124748658e89" style=3D"text-align: center;">Figure 1: EC2 In=
stances Provisioned for Dev, Prod and Jenkins</p>
<p local-id=3D"3eff0fb33687"></p>
<p local-id=3D"b7abcbd7e753">The implemented infrastructure includes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ac1b3fcf-b702-47f9-bae3-e08b73075b7a">
<li local-id=3D"462baa2e-566e-4d7e-9f93-61322acae732">
<p local-id=3D"6d857274f7f8">Jenkins Server (EC2)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0d06cc12-97c5-45cb-8819-54bba589ccda">
<p local-id=3D"ab4e899666cc">IAM Role for Jenkins</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fa93bf6e-62a3-4bd8-9b7c-2895be0c6e4c">
<p local-id=3D"ab9201202797">Dev EC2 Instance</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f002c909-10ac-44b5-91db-dc57b23fe3d4">
<p local-id=3D"cc039b9ca3cd">Prod EC2 Instance</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d8a5bf14-10be-4efa-b863-f1830f0c10fc">
<p local-id=3D"fab98a563e3b">ECS Fargate Cluster</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f61c745e-e917-46c9-b194-76d8fdfe24b2">
<p local-id=3D"0ab017b07615">ECS Service</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cd225a98-1156-407d-99df-9f38f78c052e">
<p local-id=3D"76c73b3ab324">Task Definition (NGINX container)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"17ac59e0-4122-474f-b6ed-8fa6a82138bb">
<p local-id=3D"dc132ab431ca">AWS CLI integration</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"a5b20fdb-5e0c-431b-8dbb-edf5f5cc7f1f">
<p local-id=3D"a5712e53dddd"><strong>3.2 Environments</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"1ece4c5557c6"><strong>Development Environment</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ecb8a7ec-428f-4c73-9299-8b621c5f93c0">
<li local-id=3D"8845b39b-edcd-4e61-8112-7cc07bc19eac">
<p local-id=3D"fffc92cab222">EC2 instance tagged env=3Ddev</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7b543073-a34a-4cd4-8dfc-188d4d56733d">
<p local-id=3D"16a122e5f0e8">Controlled via Jenkins pipelines</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"14eb5d053a53"><strong>Production Environment</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"7eefcae1-b091-4d6f-8ad0-2236bfcc4459">
<li local-id=3D"e16efaee-115c-4f44-8cc4-06313c60cfce">
<p local-id=3D"1a000f2d7c56">EC2 instance tagged env=3Dprod</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bfa637f6-b6ed-48a5-8c93-a1250067a787">
<p local-id=3D"71c64892de8e">Isolated from development</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"77449cad-f26c-40b2-96c6-f55d24b6b498">
<p local-id=3D"4da04fc84ce8">Controlled separately</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"69366bb6c46d"><strong>Containerized Service Environment</str=
ong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"530e7fdb-1a1d-4b8c-867d-b6ad3d3ad5e1">
<li local-id=3D"6ebe3ede-447e-4e07-85b1-fab59a76f3fb">
<p local-id=3D"0df5947e176a">ECS Fargate cluster</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"051677f6-87e6-4b76-9b7b-d1f08d8fc7bf">
<p local-id=3D"84879f6bb60f">Single service running nginx container</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"d58f5f7e-e343-424f-b816-4ab57bd280e9">
<p local-id=3D"f3326f34111a">Desired task count controlled by Jenkins</p></=
li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"51b3e424-086c-4b72-b243-150d81cb40d0">
