<p local-id=3D"b65006c3dc4a" style=3D"text-align: center;">Figure 2: ECS Fa=
rgate Cluster and Service Overview</p>
<p local-id=3D"b85405efa7bf"><strong>Secured User Request Flow</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"f4261d60-2c09-4a86-8390-05a956717389">
<li local-id=3D"4085e7c3-45d9-4ff4-903d-213e557c2103">
<p local-id=3D"4ffd06e98106">User triggers Jenkins pipeline.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c8251d6b-f988-485c-bdd3-74be0be11f24">
<p local-id=3D"a67daad6a528">Jenkins executes AWS CLI command.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e2a74cd4-ad3f-4ca3-934d-91c2f99fb717">
<p local-id=3D"f5eac1a665d9">IAM role authorizes the request.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9088bfc4-012b-4174-af7d-7297c8efdd7d">
<p local-id=3D"cc5dc241beb1">AWS updates EC2 state or ECS service desired c=
ount.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5055d291-15c7-4ddb-ac8c-92e405da1b42">
<p local-id=3D"b92a722969e0">Infrastructure state changes are validated in =
AWS Console.</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"6dce49aa-c6d7-4b32-84ef-1cb0d13a5389">
<p local-id=3D"c60fd6b7378a"><strong>3.4 Tools and Technologies</strong></p=
>
<ul local-id=3D"e6e52b12-1a06-45e8-a312-bdcac5076ba7">
<li local-id=3D"894eac6f-a4f2-4de6-b92c-f736b191ec8e">
<p local-id=3D"f217536bdcfa">AWS EC2</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"11304c52-673b-4686-8056-d4f8ab91854a">
<p local-id=3D"8628eca341da">AWS ECS (Fargate)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8a69d383-89b8-4b80-8f66-a637529374ab">
<p local-id=3D"0260b978746a">AWS IAM</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"879625f0-54fa-4c4d-b70c-2bd17e798c17">
<p local-id=3D"266e52ea7662">Jenkins</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2cbf28dc-8536-4adb-80ae-77b6614c972e">
<p local-id=3D"85ea4ea6bf33">AWS CLI</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fbabfdf5-fe74-48b5-8ae2-ac5573ea6cc5">
<p local-id=3D"ff10618fc200">Amazon Linux</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0cae58c0-8472-48a5-b488-cefc91cfbe62">
<p local-id=3D"09b3ea2c58ea">NGINX container image</p></li>
</ul>
<h1 local-id=3D"41fab2f4f5ae" id=3D"T2-TechnicalDocument-4.DevelopmentPract=
ices">4. Development Practices</h1>
<p local-id=3D"90a7624397da"><strong>4.1 Version Control</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"d78ad88bc5ed">Automation logic is implemented using Jenkins =
declarative pipelines. Infrastructure commands are embedded directly in pip=
eline scripts.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"b4f9374d-a338-4c78-9789-b685ebffb088">
<p local-id=3D"2fce78fc2719"><strong>4.2 Continuous Integration</strong></p=
>
<p local-id=3D"27c6991f03ba">Jenkins pipelines execute:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"d9ae3c8c-8f79-4bad-993c-f18f85e65619">
<li local-id=3D"ed32658b-57b5-4153-a088-37a7d0bd2b3b">
<p local-id=3D"23aaf4eab550">EC2 start/stop commands</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ca1719ec-152b-4e12-b524-df9a0dd02c24">
<p local-id=3D"6f603a2a8d6a">ECS service scaling commands</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bf39a74d-089a-4e2e-877a-c3264c4db43d">
<p local-id=3D"dc452ba32359">State verification via CLI</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f87b143012e9">Each execution produces console logs confirmin=
g success or failure.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"1a159d99-15d7-4fd0-a0f9-121b3265e1b2">
<p local-id=3D"3c89f8d0bf26"><strong>4.3 Automated Testing</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"8b1bb536919f">Operational validation includes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"aef214eb-5533-4e67-a030-b2522868e7c5">
<li local-id=3D"49528410-6809-4d0c-9e17-74bf6485e587">
<p local-id=3D"c2aac3312dea">Verifying EC2 state transitions (Stopped =E2=
=86=94 Running)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"557af316-7aa3-4757-943d-a1c6ff6afb27">
<p local-id=3D"f35136945c9a">Verifying ECS desired count changes (0 =E2=86=
=94 1)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"35cfe868-228c-44de-b13d-01a53483c804">
<p local-id=3D"d34c0d795b8b">Monitoring running task count in ECS</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"530b4d20-e27a-4227-89ea-c44bf9c6c5ab">
<p local-id=3D"6a93f04cdb30"><strong>4.4 Code Quality and Analysis</strong>=
</p>
<p local-id=3D"ace3553a7c47">Pipelines were structured using:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"8dfb7b33-e5c2-47fd-90d8-06536ccc29f2">
<li local-id=3D"7920efa6-1b79-406a-a5c9-2f6022c38024">
<p local-id=3D"c1ec87728659">Declarative syntax</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0b253698-26f8-4c93-b6da-026b8beface9">
<p local-id=3D"a022e6ac33b0">Clear CLI command separation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"83d9ad73-6115-4477-9a32-851d40035802">
<p local-id=3D"f96ecdb03e40">Explicit region definition</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2856a409-1312-4545-835d-5e63b130a170">
<p local-id=3D"6977dfde5b06">Console logging for traceability</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"a900db3c-7877-4df1-95e2-93fd5928749a">
<h1 local-id=3D"b173e7a9b256" id=3D"T2-TechnicalDocument-5.DeploymentandRel=
easeManagement">5. Deployment and Release Management</h1>
<p local-id=3D"349fd8ca4242"><strong>5.1 Deployment Strategy</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"57ec922c6ba7">ECS deployment uses:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"86f2a778-bc63-4893-b5ef-499f0cc7f6be">
<li local-id=3D"886eb1fc-9d1c-40df-a799-f07ed706bf0c">
<p local-id=3D"68ea6c9af96a">Desired task count scaling</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3af448a0-00cf-4fd5-b234-09ebad494d6d">
<p local-id=3D"e55e0a073444">AWS-managed task provisioning</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5c71aa1b-cd35-40d8-b738-25b5b81ec5e5">
<p local-id=3D"2f769ca7e34e">Automatic container lifecycle handling</p></li=
>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"6317e4498045">EC2 deployment uses:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"36d9df73-3d3b-4a26-8c21-c7d4cd7c7e18">
<li local-id=3D"72ea73cb-e079-4a90-bf87-36027ba280b6">
<p local-id=3D"8c9ce7464c87">Controlled start and stop lifecycle management=
</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"10d74c62-b7fd-4640-a6c8-a6e6d0126b2f">
<p local-id=3D"1a38a070c66b"><strong>5.2 Configuration Management</strong><=
/p>
<p local-id=3D"0f8a83bf8b96">Configuration handled through:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"a51af272-8232-49e9-a763-ecae67c263f3">
<li local-id=3D"7b2edeb5-ad29-4311-82ab-32347f72316d">
<p local-id=3D"97c4a4d5545b">AWS Console provisioning</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5f0d75b9-6719-41fc-8f61-4ce54ce1f09c">
<p local-id=3D"c736c92f8ac9">IAM policy definitions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6f6e2726-4d84-4722-b766-a8e333ab1160">
<p local-id=3D"20f9a370949c">Jenkins declarative pipeline scripts</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e1031037-0dbe-4303-9237-88003ce9f1e7">
<p local-id=3D"84f1822ec865">AWS CLI commands</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"5bf6ebea-99e4-47f9-a735-d7b765105454">
