<p local-id=3D"326dc0ac6f4b"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"ac44df61fe54">Infrastructure control is automated via Jenkin=
s pipelines, enabling repeatable execution of start and stop operations acr=
oss environments.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"1cf77334-2d01-4cc1-a04f-075db8864b24">
<h1 local-id=3D"56feef70bd95" id=3D"T2-TechnicalDocument-6.MonitoringandInc=
identManagement">6. Monitoring and Incident Management</h1>
<p local-id=3D"332bfb4297a3"><strong>6.1 Monitoring Tools and Metrics</stro=
ng></p>
<p local-id=3D"8ad13dce788b">Monitoring performed via:</p>
