<p local-id=3D"6978af174734"><strong>6.2 Alerting and Notification</strong>=
</p>
<p local-id=3D"90e8f1ae1e8b">Pipeline execution status provides:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b23649e2-b09d-4cf9-8b2f-4eaa4c03f080">
<li local-id=3D"ebf1d71a-46e5-47b9-981e-d8c29ae254c3">
<p local-id=3D"c3d01ba73dd1">Immediate success/failure visibility</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6938292e-1a46-4d7a-8aca-a2b359b15e77">
<p local-id=3D"1fa618b9cd8b">Console logs for troubleshooting</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"3aee8ddf-fb25-4f6f-bfed-090c0a6acc64">
<p local-id=3D"500d1a7d7be3"><strong>6.3 Incident Management</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"9865c7c2f640">Incident handling process:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"943bbd0c-379c-4c85-9103-aaf27b6fe76d">
<li local-id=3D"2cc83303-3fb6-4555-a82a-f3c6ccc5593d">
<p local-id=3D"92baa6c7759d">Identify failure from Jenkins build log.</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"ce337ba1-966a-4514-a2da-222a89e0f37d">
<p local-id=3D"399ea1fc6d3b">Verify AWS resource state.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4035fd70-0220-4dc8-9d9c-27195b523afa">
<p local-id=3D"00c5a601ee79">Re-run pipeline if required.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"de0687b1-cbf5-4b94-86c8-ff7075fda527">
<p local-id=3D"191557d1ab86">Confirm state correction.</p></li>
</ol>
