<h1 local-id=3D"83894247a97d" id=3D"T2-TechnicalDocument-8.CostOptimization=
">8. Cost Optimization</h1>
<p local-id=3D"aa64a1b72fcb"><strong>Cost Control Mechanisms Implemented</s=
trong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ef19b680-550c-47fe-b707-bdf34268c146">
<li local-id=3D"3f07f121-cad7-4365-9182-5e0a35682ed7">
<p local-id=3D"0bba08bec75a">EC2 instances stopped when not in use</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"24db24bf-0e7c-40ff-a650-0bc9c000fd41">
<p local-id=3D"26083e907297">ECS Fargate service scaled to zero when idle</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7fdec70d-9f39-47f5-b4df-fc7752be72da">
<p local-id=3D"382cc858e071">Serverless container model reduces idle comput=
e costs</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"13e09254f065"><strong>Inputs Used for Cost Estimation</stron=
g></p>
<ul local-id=3D"1414782b-9b38-45a8-b3c5-968f20babe91">
<li local-id=3D"706fbdf7-0163-4794-b716-435b7e143910">
<p local-id=3D"6bf36fb8b9c3">EC2 instance type (t2.micro)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8dfdffd6-a7b6-4ee8-8c8a-2134ee8ad8de">
<p local-id=3D"6603e704b90c">Fargate CPU and memory allocation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"85a36492-6680-4d1c-ba5d-9766f71da073">
<p local-id=3D"994a8e144478">Estimated runtime duration</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"c0019c350392"><strong>Business Value Delivered</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"3bc55d2b-3f98-4e3e-ace5-ad941fc69b21">
<li local-id=3D"ddc42bb8-269b-46d8-ac68-1a81f3660272">
<p local-id=3D"a5c245e23d30">Reduced infrastructure wastage</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5f5cd011-7c9f-4e6a-9f5e-69e18cd6e5f9">
<p local-id=3D"2052389af5dd">Controlled cloud spending</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cc10f7b9-714b-477b-9ba3-866631ee0a83">
<p local-id=3D"75154116fdc5">Operational efficiency through automation</p><=
/li>
</ul>
