<h1 local-id=3D"093c9afe2894" id=3D"T2-TechnicalDocument-11.ContinuousImpro=
vement">11. Continuous Improvement</h1>
<p local-id=3D"903c9c44e5b0"><strong>11.1 Feedback and Retrospectives</stro=
ng></p>
<p local-id=3D"762bdec6ed80">Implementation was reviewed based on:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"de28831f-aeef-4585-b429-f9753cfeb1e1">
<li local-id=3D"bf981d3c-43b7-4646-822d-d02702fe757c">
<p local-id=3D"a651b5568743">Security validation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"48663059-e858-41d9-9d47-6bf3406ae651">
<p local-id=3D"aec35fde6c28">Automation accuracy</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f2561e36-f56f-4e45-9f6b-664f7f1a2daa">
<p local-id=3D"e3cf85b5117b">Infrastructure state verification</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"19739ad5-22cf-403b-8f40-3457f2f0edf5">
<p local-id=3D"9979e689a684"><strong>11.2 Iterative Enhancements</strong></=
p>
<p local-id=3D"58b1cc52f795">Automation refined to ensure stable execution =
and accurate service scaling behavior.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"826fb188-33d1-4970-b69e-6f881078a98f">
<h1 local-id=3D"68080bf41549" id=3D"T2-TechnicalDocument-12.Conclusion">12.=
 Conclusion</h1>
<p local-id=3D"db95ca7d7030"><strong>12.1 Summary</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"a0696a0b7713">The solution successfully demonstrates secure =
and automated infrastructure lifecycle management using Jenkins integrated =
with AWS services.</p>
<p local-id=3D"e96cf0e3de35">Key achievements:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"012c1f9a-b46d-4734-bc93-73cac42169e8">
<li local-id=3D"e4ac82ad-40bb-458d-8a6c-3e2c525e8314">
<p local-id=3D"e0e94c32e0c2">Secure IAM-based authentication</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"67da72e0-8a27-4ca5-a327-2a908630f562">
<p local-id=3D"a5a1ec81a3c6">Automated EC2 lifecycle control</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8d98ea62-f92b-43a8-855c-6f5b3c2646a3">
<p local-id=3D"ecafa336a776">Automated ECS Fargate service scaling</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"abf54f33-e3a2-47c5-9b2c-132486b27035">
<p local-id=3D"52923853cc75">Cost-optimized infrastructure usage</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dab08544-e1b5-4802-9f99-817d67593def">
<p local-id=3D"a233431fb0d4">Operational visibility through logs</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"9458b6e10fa0"><strong>12.2 Next Steps</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"bf3e55589d3c">Implementation has achieved defined objectives=
 within scope.</p>
